lines.text: Hello? Is it here you get killed?

[while talking behind her back, Alexandra all of a sudden appears in front of Tim, giving him a big scare]
Did I scare you?
No I usually shit my pants this time of the evening
How often do you get the chance to get murdered?

[in a high pitched voice]
Jonas is gonna die! Jonas is gonna die!
Aia goddamnit! If people are crazy, then they are it even if they have played a crazy game or not!
What kind of monster have done this?
